# Deterministic bytes across platforms. The log, canonical serialization,
# and golden vectors are hash-ratcheted (versioning.md) - CRLF churn would
# break every hash and the frozen shell hooks. Normalize everything to LF.
* text=auto eol=lf
*.sh        text eol=lf
scripts/*   text eol=lf
*.go        text eol=lf
*.json      text eol=lf
